em': to use the same shadowbox for an item, ='individual': to use a shadowbox only for this image, other value= to set the group of images of the shadowbox ; \t\t\t\t<dd>images are stored in img/trackers; \t\t\t\t<dd>multiple options must appear in the order specified, separated by commas. \t\t\t\t</dl>",
